The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 slow and steady

 - first look

 Produced by Anjum Rizvi and directed by debutant Shivam Nair, Ahista Ahista is a bitter-sweet tale of love where Soha Ali Khan plays a small-town girl who elopes to the city with her boyfriend, played by Shayan Munshi. When Shayan betrays her, Soha finds love in the arms of Abhay Deol. Shot in Nainital and New Delhi, Ahista Ahista is slated to release in June.




